data.description:
*REDUCED PRICE*Welcome to Fox Creek Subdivision, a delightful residential area boasting a charming home with four bedrooms and two full bathrooms. Built in 2002, the house features a private fence and a covered patio, creating a tranquil retreat for outdoor relaxation. Equipped with paid in full solar panels, this eco-friendly residence embraces sustainable living.
Situated conveniently in the heart of the city, this home offers easy access to various amenities. Residents enjoy the proximity to schools, shopping centers, a mall, and a hospital, ensuring convenience in everyday life. The house itself comprises a cozy living room, a dining area, and a kitchen with a breakfast bar, facilitating comfortable family living and entertaining. While inside, you'll notice ceramic tile throughout the entire house, lending a stylish and low-maintenance touch to the interior. Experience the comfort, convenience, and aesthetic appeal of this exceptional home.
